 matches. Gun Run Team Composition: There are 4 teams in total, each composed of 1 participant from each country. Gameplay: The 4 teams compete in Gun Run mode. Fight Night Team Composition: A total of 10 participants are selected to compete at the designated place on the designated map. Gameplay: All the 10 competitors arrive at the place of Fight Night in Olympus within a limited time and fight against each other in the boxing ring. Only the props provided by loot rollers are allowed to use. The last standing player wins. Random Mode Team Composition: There are 20 teams in total, each composed of 3 participants including 1 cross-game creator and 2 specialized Apex Legends streamers. Gameplay: Maps, characters, and weapons are determined in a match according to the result of random throwing; other items can be used freely. The champion team wins. Learn more about Apex Legends Asia Festival: www.apexasiafes.com ",
